      <title>美国两年期国债收益率在美国 CPI 公布前接近 2022 年以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/treasury-two-year-yield-nears-lowest-since-2022-ahead-of-us-cpi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债价格上涨，推动两年期国债收益率跌至 2022 年以来的最低水平，而备受关注的通胀数据可能会巩固对货币宽松的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/treasury-two-year-yield-nears-lowest-since-2022-ahead-of-us-cpi</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 07:40:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚在国内美元债券拍卖中筹集 9 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/nigeria-raises-900-million-in-domestic-dollar-bond-auction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚政府在国内首次拍卖美元计价债券中筹集了 9 亿美元，几乎是目标金额的两倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/nigeria-raises-900-million-in-domestic-dollar-bond-auction</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 07:32:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国通胀和欧洲央行会议前，欧洲股市小幅走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/european-stocks-tick-higher-ahead-of-us-inflation-ecb-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市小幅走高，投资者等待周三晚些时候公布的敏感美国通胀数据，以便为美联储近期政策举措提供线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/european-stocks-tick-higher-ahead-of-us-inflation-ecb-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 07:30:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德与意大利财政部就管理 30 亿欧元进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/blackrock-in-talks-with-italy-s-sace-on-managing-3-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，贝莱德公司正在与意大利国家贸易信用保险公司进行谈判，以管理高达 30 亿欧元（33 亿美元）的资产，此举可能增强这家美国资产管理公司在欧元区第三大经济体中的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/blackrock-in-talks-with-italy-s-sace-on-managing-3-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 07:21:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港修改“市场试探”规则，加重银行负担</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/hong-kong-revises-market-sounding-rules-to-put-burden-on-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，香港证券监管机构计划在年底前发布市场试探指引，根据市场参与者的反馈，修改之前的草案，减少规定性规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/hong-kong-revises-market-sounding-rules-to-put-burden-on-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 07:20:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
